You are an expert fullstack developer. Build a complete Fast Food Restaurant POS & Accounting System using only Vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript on the frontend — no frameworks.

---

## TECH STACK
- Frontend: Vanilla HTML + CSS + JavaScript (ES6+ modules)
- Backend: Node.js + Express.js
- Database: MongoDB with Mongoose
- Libraries allowed (CDN):
  - qrcode.js → QR code generation
  - Chart.js → dashboard charts

---

## PROJECT STRUCTURE

```
/fastfood-pos
  /frontend
    index.html          → cashier (main POS)
    products.html       → product management
    dashboard.html      → statistics & reports
    /css
      style.css
    /js
      cashier.js
      products.js
      dashboard.js
      api.js            → all fetch() calls in one place
  /backend
    /models
      Product.js
      Order.js
    /routes
      products.js
      orders.js
    /controllers
      products.controller.js
      orders.controller.js
    server.js
  .env
  README.md
```

---

## DESIGN SYSTEM (apply to all pages)

- Background: #F9F9F9
- Primary accent: #FF6B35 (orange)
- Text: #1A1A1A
- Card background: #FFFFFF with box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
- Border radius: 10px on cards, 6px on buttons and inputs
- Font: system-ui, sans-serif
- Nav: fixed left sidebar, 220px wide, white background, icons + labels
- Active nav item: accent color background, white text
- Buttons: solid accent color, white text, no border, cursor pointer
- Inputs: border 1px solid #E0E0E0, padding 8px 12px, focus border accent color
- Keep it clean and minimal — no heavy decorations, no gradients

